items.name: Transposition Anvil
items.description: This structure is used by the C.A.A. to fabricate powerful weapons.

items.name: Pet Food Kibble
items.description: A simple, preserved type of kibble. Not an effective taming food, but an excellent, easy-to-make pet food to fill your troughs. Almost anything will eat it.

items.name: Alpha Blood
items.description: Blood from an Additional Alpha. Its genetic makeup is very strange, but it has some practical purposes, regardless of the non-viable material therin.

items.name: Mangrove Tree Wood
items.description: A thick, sturdy cutting from a swamp tree, such as a mangrove or cypress.

items.name: Redwood Tree Wood
items.description: A thick, sturdy cutting from a redwood tree.

items.name: Genome Assembly
items.description: A modified stasis chamber used to manufacture genetic life.

items.name: Gasball to Gasoline
items.description: A chemical process which can turn Congealed Gas Balls into Gasoline.

items.name: Sciences Table
items.description: Looks a bit rusted and rough, but that's what you get on the arks. It's a reliable station to help you learn some sciences that'll give you an edge of survival. Requires electrical power, as well as additional gasoline power in inventory.

items.name: Huntsman's Boomerang
items.description: Straight from the outback of ARKstralia, this isnt the typical toy you're used to. One good throw from this aboriginal weapon, if it doesnt kill, will knock any small-to-mid sized creature on it's rear or leave it winded.

items.name: Wooden Spear Bolt
items.description: A spear that has been shortened, able to be fired from a bow. It deals great damage.  If it doesn't break, you can recover your ammo.

items.name: Mothball Grenade
items.description: Pulling the pin starts a 5 second timer to an explosion.  Make sure you've thrown it by then. Causes no damage, but effects similar to Lymantria spores. Useful for speeding up passive tames.

items.name: .500 Magnum
items.description: The .500 Magnum is the King of all Revolvers, a death sentence to anything unfortunate enough to be caught at the business end of the it. The C.A.A. has used unique materials to turn this gun from a novel collector's item into a practical revolver. Alarmingly reliable and durable, the only downside to this gun is its weight and the expensive upkeep. It can even fire underwater.

items.name: .408 Ammo
items.description: A large-caliber bullet created to be lighter and faster then a .50 Cal round.

items.name: .408 Ammo SCR
items.description: Specialy designed Super Cavitation Rounds are designed to allow weapons to be viable for shooting into or below water.

items.name: .500 Ammo
items.description: A large-caliber bullet designed for taking down large animals, or for pure overkill.

items.name: .500 SCR Ammo
items.description: Specialy designed Super Cavitation Rounds are designed to allow weapons to be viable for shooting into or below water.

items.name: 5.56x45mm NATO
items.description: A medium-caliber modern bullet, primarily used by NATO.

items.name: 7.62x39mm Ammo
items.description: A large caliber bullet, its heavy weight can cause heavy damage at cost to stability.

items.name: 9mm Ammo
items.description: A small caliber bullet used by many PDWs.

items.name: Co2 Cartridge
items.description: Contains highly compressed carbon dioxide.

items.name: Empty Co2 Cartridge
items.description: Refill with carbon dioxide at the Transposition Anvil.

items.name: 9mm Ammo
items.description: A potent dart full of tranquilizer poisen. For use with a DI-Tranquilizer Rifle.

items.name: M4A1
items.description: The M4A1 Carbine is a Military grade assult rifle. Excellent Accuracy and Rate of Fire makes this weapon one to be reckoned with.

items.name: C.A.A Samurai Edge
items.description: An adapted form of Fabricated Pistol made by G.S.R. Wraith. Used by C.A.A. agents, it sacrifices nothing for the sake of being a dependable sidearm. Its firing power is similar to that of a simple pistol.

items.name: Flamethrower (C.A.A Variant)
items.description: An adapted flamethrower model built by G.S.R. Wraith. Its potency compared to the base model is far more lethal.

items.name: MP5k
items.description: Built for close quarter engagments and conceled carry. This SMG is cappable of firing at 900rpm, which makes it perfect for riddeling anything with many holes in a short amount of time. Lightweight and easy to conceal. Focus fire to devastate targets.

items.name: Carbon
items.description: With the help of the Transpotion Anvil, small traces of carbon can be extracted from charcoal.

items.name: Steel Ingot
items.description: Refined steel that proves to be a very durable alloy and is great from crafting military grade weapons.

items.name: Tungsten
items.description: With the help of the Transpotion Anvil, small traces of Tungsten can be extracted from the ARKs metal ores.

items.name: AK-47
items.description: The AK-47 is renowned for being sturdy, rugged and cheap to manufacture. What it lacks in stability, it makes up for with raw power. This rugged, reliable gun can even fire underwater.

items.name: M4A1
items.description: The M4A1 Carbine is a Military grade assult rifle. Excellent Accuracy and Rate of Fire makes this weapon one to be reckoned with. This is the most widely used assault rifle in the C.A.A, and for good reason.

items.name: C.A.A. Wraithsfinger
items.description: An adapted form of the Fabricated Sniper Rifle, made by G.S.R. Wraith. Drastically overhauls durability for maximum field use, while increasing firepower considerable differences.. This is a gun that kills.

items.name: Incendary RPG Round
items.description:
This ammo type deals reduced damage compared to a normal rocket round (but more to herbivores because it is not an explosive damage type), but sets the target ablaze. The reduced volitile firepower greatly reduces wear and tear on the launcher.

Sometimes if you can't blow something up, it's better to just watch it burn.

items.name: Muhreetle
items.description: Used by primitive tribes, this spiked club has extremely short range but is absolutely brutal, thanks to the keratinous spines adorning it; which also allow it to penetrate armor & bleed out its victims. Rated 10/10 Ooga for your Booga by brawlers

items.name: Prime Dart
items.description: A shock dart, increased in potency with the strange Alpha Blood material found in Additional Alphas. Never spoils, easier to carry, 3x potency of shock darts

items.name: Improved Tranq Dart
items.description: A potent dart for when you can't wait for Shock Darts. Between normal and Shocking in potency. Roughly 1/2 times stronger than normal darts!

items.name: Create Harvester Mech
items.description: Build and construct a massive Harvester Mech: Deisgned by the C.A.A. to assist in harvesting resources (mineral preferrably), Be warned: IT'S HEAVY!

items.name: Robotics Diesel
items.description: Refined Gasoline used in powering advanced robotics
